reviewText: The photographer is good, but not great in my opinion and other than being beautiful, the models aren't great either.  Just another marketing thing to get people to pay for a brochure I guess.  I had hoped it would be more interesting with Photoflex's brand name attached to it like that on the cover.  About the only thing that helps it is that it has a few good behind the scenes segments on how to use some light modifiers for photographers who don't know what they are doing.
